data.name: txt_Two.Text
data.value:
The remaining amount of money can be seen in top left corner of the game. After winning a bet, depending on the bet type, you will earn additional money.
Moreover, after selecting the desired betting amount, you will see the actual chip displayed on the bet you've chosen. Note that only one chip can be placed on one spot at a time.
Adding an additional chip cannot be done unless the bet is canceled. You can cancel the bet by simply double clicking the chip and choosing a different betting amount. That will refund the money that was set on this bet and you will be able to choose different betting amount.
